  "texts": [
    "Additionally, one can envision that LLMs could be finetuned to adapt their style to the user via prompt engineering.",
    "By default, models such as ChatGPT have a verbose and rather academic writing style.",
    "In summary, we believe that LLMs can be useful for the collation and reformulation of generic information as well as information specifically related to dementia.",
    "In the latter case, finetuned models such as Med-PaLM will likely be required.",
    "Furthermore, care needs to be taken to avoid blurring the line between a conversational service and medical advice, since at least for the time being healthcare professionals should be the ultimate source of medical advice."
  ],
